text: The Woodlands is a master planned community and census-designated place (CDP) in the U.S. state of Texas, in the Houston–The Woodlands–Sugar Land metropolitan area. It is primarily located in Montgomery County, with parts going into Harris County. In 2020, the population of The Woodlands was 114,436. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in Harris County, Texas
title: The Woodlands, Texas
